Author: Cfighters
Title: [ANN] [ICO] Pre-ICO for the CryptoGame CFighters
Body: At this moment, we are working in the Pre-ICO. In the future there will be an ICO but not a Bounty. The game is based on Ethereum Tokens and we believe that it is more successful to do it in the blockchain ecosystem from the beginning. Thanks for asking!
